ey made her senior debut with Kerr's iconic number 20 jersey in line with the Olympics rules for players to only wear numbers between one and 22.\", \"from\": 925, \"to\": 1122, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 943, \"end\": 951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Sam Kerr\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Sam_Kerr\"}, {\"begin\": 965, \"end\": 979, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_Torpey\", \"score\": 0.9999998507119128, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kaitlyn Torpey\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_Torpey\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kaitlyn_Torpey\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's amazing, my emotions are high right now, just trying to take it all in...\", \"from\": 1124, \"to\": 1203, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so happy,\\\" Torpey said.\", \"from\": 1204, \"to\": 1232, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's just so nice to be back with the girls, back playing for my country and to come on and score a goal, it's a dream come true\\\" \\u00f0\\u0178\\u00a5\\u00b9\\u00f0\\u0178\\u017d\\u00a4 Hear from Michelle Heyman post-match following our 3-0 win over Uzbekistan.\\u00f0\\u0178\\u017d\\u00a5:@10FootballAU#Matildas#TilitsDone#AllezAUS#Paris2024pic.twitter.com/OiHbZ49B8L  Matildas coach Tony Gustavsson switched up his attack strategy with Torpey coming off and Caitlin Foord coming on, which proved effective.\", \"from\": 1234, \"to\": 1672, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1384, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"score\": 0.9996508794537684, \"rank\": 0.000338701777282627, \"text\": \"Michelle\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michelle_Fowler\", \"dbpedia\": \"ht